# CLEENLY

> CLEENLY is a house cleaning booking platform serving Seattle and the Greater Eastside (Washington State). Customers can book cleaning services online, see prices before booking, and choose their preferred cleaner.

## Services
- Regular Cleaning: routine maintenance cleaning for homes
- Deep Cleaning: thorough cleaning including appliances, baseboards, and hard-to-reach areas
- Move-Out Cleaning: landlord-ready cleaning to help get security deposits back

## Service Areas
Seattle, Bellevue, Kirkland, Redmond, Renton, Kent, Tacoma, Everett, and surrounding cities in Washington State.

## Pricing
- Regular Cleaning: $100-$200 depending on home size
- Deep Cleaning: $150-$300 depending on home size
- Move-Out Cleaning: $200-$400 depending on home size
